-section-color-overlay' style='opacity: 0.4; background-color: #ffffff; '><\/div><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-1423'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>\n<div class=\"flex_column av_one_fifth  av-hide-on-mobile  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-3  el_before_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-first  left-third \" style='background: #ffffff; border-width:1px; border-color:#ffffff; border-style:solid; padding:12px; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:2px; '><\/div><div class=\"flex_column av_three_fifth  avia-full-contain flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-4  el_after_av_one_fifth  el_before_av_one_fifth  \" style='background: #ffffff; border-width:1px; border-color:#ffffff; border-style:solid; box-shadow: 0 0 2px 0 #9e9e9e; padding:12px; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:2px; '><section class=\"av_textblock_section \"  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><h3>Shopping<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">J<\/span>ust a stone\u2019s throw from the beach lies the\u00a0Malibu Country Mart, a premier seaside destination for shopping, dining, and relaxing. The Malibu Country Mart features upscale boutiques, restaurants, and personal services set in a calming, laid-back setting.<\/p>\n<p>With its beautiful open-air layout, distinctive Mediterranean architecture, lavish landscaping and dynamic fountains filled with koi fish and turtles, The Commons at Calabasas is the ultimate in neighborhood shopping, dining and entertainment.<\/p>\n<p>Only 18 miles away is Beverly Hills\u2019 Rodeo Drive, the crown jewel of luxury shopping and eating.<\/p>\n<h3>Food<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">R<\/span>ight in the middle of wine country is Calamigos Ranch&#8217;s Malibu Caf\u00e9. Bring your dogs and spend the day cocktailing and dining at tables on grass lawns listening to live music or have a more intimate meal in one of the personal private settings around the ranch.<\/p>\n<p>Other local restaurants of note include\u00a0Nobu, exquisite Japanese cuisine with sushi bar and ocean front lounge;\u00a0Mastro\u2019s, world-class steakhouse and seafood restaurant on the water;\u00a0The Old Place, rustic restaurant and bar cooking almost everything over a red oak fire;\u00a0Nonna, authentic Italian cuisine and Malibu Farm Pier Cafe, a farm to table restaurant overlooking the water.<\/p>\n<h3>Schools<\/h3>\n<p>Within 10-minutes of Malibu Valley are some of the most outstanding schools in the state. The Las Virgenes United School District (LVUSD) has been recognized as both US\u00a0Blue\u00a0Ribbon\u00a0&#038;\u00a0CA\u00a0Gold\u00a0Ribbon\u00a0schools. Private schools such as Viewpoint, Sierra Canyon, and Oaks Christian are all nationally recognized college preparatory schools.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div><div class=\"flex_column av_one_fifth  av-hide-on-mobile  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-6  el_after_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-last  right-third \" style='background: #ffffff; border-width:1px; border-color:#ffffff; border-style:solid; padding:12px; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:2px; '><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1586,"parent":46,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1423"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1423"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1